    "Finally, in Sect. 6, we outline future research directions specifically from the viewpoint of model fusion and complementary learning paradigms.",
    "This paper is a focused survey, assessing only the aforementioned coupled subfields, of which learning paradigms make the learned models more robust, and model fusion brings those models together.",
    "For a more wide-ranging survey into federated learning, we recommend readers to refer [107][108][109].",
    "Related surveySeveral related surveys have been published in recent years, as summarized in Table 2.",
    "This section introduces the existing surveys and highlights our survey's contributions to the literature."
